entries.category: The Clone Relics, Fist of the Empire
entries.journal_entry_description: You stumbled upon classified Rebel data. Things can only get better from here on... or can they?
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The Empire's scouts have spotted a Rebel supply convoy in what's known as Kkowir forest. The scout troopers will provide you with a waypoint to their location. Make sure that convoy never reaches its destination. When you're done, return to Admiral Krieg.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Take care of the Rebels in the name of the Emperor!
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Return to the Imperial base next to Kachirho. Good job soldier!
